From 1 (least ethical) to 5 (most ethical), evaluate the following policies proposed for ABC.

 current policy: reported earnings are biased by 50 cents and investors are not misled as they correctly anticipate the bias.
 new policy: reported earnings are unbiased and some investors may incorrectly assume that reported earnings are biased.
